# Per-instance Dovecot overlay for mail1.test.
#
# Mounted at /etc/dovecot-overlay; merged on top of the baked-in
# /etc/dovecot/conf.d/*.conf defaults at startup. Drop *.conf files here to
# tweak auth, namespaces, plugins, or quota policy for this instance only.
#
# Empty by default — defaults shipped with reference-dovecot are enough for
# the seeded SQL-backed virtual mailboxes.
